"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2486854-modi-watched-as-arshad-nadeem-made-history-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"US  Following Neeraj Chopra's silver medal win, Indian PM personally called him at around 1am to offer 'congratulations'  Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi was among the millions who witnessed Pakistan's Arshad Nadeem clinch gold in the javelin throw at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.7524282989838368, \"rank\": 0.29474920986892184, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian Prime Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9963765165762561, \"rank\": 0.0036280622499412617, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event, which captured global attention, saw Nadeem making history with a record-breaking throw of 92.97 metres, securing Pakistan's first Olympic gold in 40 years.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 410, \